name: 50k Stablepizza
description: Because it's more fun to hold a silver Pizza instead of 50k Tokens. A limited edition Pizza only available for a limited time in the RareDough Shop. Owners of this NFT are eligible to receive 50250 BREAD Tokens (0.5% Bonus), if burned in the Oven. Final supply is determined based on Sales during the Sale period. Burn-Oven is enabled AFTER Sale ends.
